The '''Sherzad tribe''' is one of the three major sub-tribes of the [[Khogyani tribe]] of [[Karlani]] [[Pashtun people|Pashtun]].  The Sherzad are primarily found in the central regions of [[Nangarhar Province]], [[Afghanistan]], particularly [[Sherzad District]]. {{citation needed|date=October 2017}}

